  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t1.<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly92b2N1cy5jYy9hcnRpY2xlLzYzZmEzZjFhZmQ4OTc4MDAwMWRlMWNhYg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://vocus.cc/article/63fa3f1afd89780001de1cab\">兵力，俄羅斯打不贏的原因</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n2.<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly92b2N1cy5jYy9hcnRpY2xlLzYzZmEzZjUzZmQ4OTc4MDAwMWRlMWQ2YQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://vocus.cc/article/63fa3f53fd89780001de1d6a\">政治，打不贏也得出兵的道理</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n3.<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly92b2N1cy5jYy9hcnRpY2xlLzYzZmEzZjg0ZmQ4OTc4MDAwMWRlMWVhZA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://vocus.cc/article/63fa3f84fd89780001de1ead\">謀算，俄羅斯有兵？動員不足的算計</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n4.<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly92b2N1cy5jYy9hcnRpY2xlLzYzZmEzZmI1ZmQ4OTc4MDAwMWRlMWY3NQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://vocus.cc/article/63fa3fb5fd89780001de1f75\">實戰，情報傳遞遲緩的慘劇</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n5.<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly92b2N1cy5jYy9hcnRpY2xlLzYzZmE0MzMxZmQ4OTc4MDAwMWRlMzcxYw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://vocus.cc/article/63fa4331fd89780001de371c\">僵持：你察覺我的察覺，我察覺你的察覺</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n6.<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly92b2N1cy5jYy9hcnRpY2xlLzYzZmE0MzVhZmQ4OTc4MDAwMWRlMzgxYQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://vocus.cc/article/63fa435afd89780001de381a\">數據，意識形態與資訊判讀</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n==============================================<br/>\r\n個人觀點：<br/>\n<br/>\r\n並非放在武器比較，而是回歸戰爭最本質的一面：戰爭是政治的延伸，而兵力與情報依然是戰爭決定性的關鍵。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n算是給非軍事迷的入門解析，為什麼俄羅斯打成這樣。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
